Package: encryptor
Version: 1.1.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: mpgamer75
Depends: openssl (>= 1.1.0), bash (>= 4.0)
Recommends: curl, wget
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/mpgamer75/encryptor
Description: Advanced file encryption tool with multiple algorithms
 Encryptor is a powerful, user-friendly command-line encryption tool that
 provides security for your files. Built with pure Bash and OpenSSL, it
 offers multiple encryption algorithms with an intuitive interface.
 .
 Features:
  - Multiple encryption algorithms: AES-256, RSA, Hybrid AES+RSA, 3DES
  - Beautiful CLI interface with colorful, intuitive menus
  - Military-grade security with industry-standard encryption
  - Cross-platform compatibility (Linux, macOS, WSL)
  - Automatic key management and secure file handling